1)aysyncronous communication and asyscronous programming are different.

2)asyncronous communication and asyncronous resource are difference.

3)HTTP support only syncronous communication.

4) HttpServletDispatcher(syncronous)(till 2.5 servlet version)

5) HttpServlet30Dispatcher(asyncronous)(3.0 servlet version)

6) we will use a AsyncResponse by using @Suspended annotation.
         AsyncResponse is a response handler class.

Note:-In aysncronous resource we use a saparate thread to execute and send back the response.

